00:06.406 --> 00:08.308 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
On the "NewsHour" tonight:

00:08.342 --> 00:10.944 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
Commuting her sentence was
entirely appropriate.

00:10.978 --> 00:15.315 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In his final news
conference,
President Obama addresses the
controversial

00:15.349 --> 00:21.355 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
