Manning and his
role in a new era of politics.

00:21.388 --> 00:27.494 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Then: The Senate takes on a
whirlwind of confirmation
hearings, grilling the
president-elect's picks

00:27.527 --> 00:29.730 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
for the next Cabinet.

00:29.763 --> 00:35.736 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
