00:37.537 --> 00:40.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHL BINDERBAUER, CTO, Tri
Alpha Energy:
Our great-great-great-grandkids
are going

00:40.173 --> 00:42.943 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
