analyst convicted
of leaking U.S. military and
diplomatic secrets.

01:31.191 --> 01:37.564 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
Chelsea Manning has served a
tough prison

01:37.597 --> 01:39.366 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
sentence.

01:39.399 --> 01:48.608 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, the notion that the average
person who
was thinking about disclosing
vital classified

01:48.642 --> 01:58.352 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
information would think that it
goes unpunished,
I don't think would get that
impression from

01:58.385 --> 02:01.722 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the sentence that Chelsea
Manning has served.

02:01.755 --> 02:06.460 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Most of the news
conference was
spent looking ahead to the fate
of his own

02:06.493 --> 02:09.563 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
accomplishments after
president-elect Trump
takes office.

02:09.596 --> 02:17.304 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
BARACK OBAMA: My working
assumption is that,
having won an election, opposed
a number of

02:17.337 --> 02:25.045 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
my initiatives and some aspects
of my vision
for where the country needs to
go, it's appropriate

02:25.078 --> 02:33.887 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
