vision and
his values.

02:33.920 --> 02:40.127 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I don't expect that there's
going to be,
you know, enormous overlap.

02:40.160 --> 02:44.398 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: He also shed light on
the counsel
he's offered Mr. Trump.

02:44.431 --> 02:51.238 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: This is a job of
such magnitude,
that you can't do it by
yourself.

02:51.271 --> 03:00.814 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
