team, your
Cabinet, your senior White House
staff, all

03:00.847 --> 03:07.421 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the way to fairly junior folks
in their 20s
and 30s, but who are executing
on significant

03:07.454 --> 03:09.156 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
responsibilities.

03:09.189 --> 03:15.295 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's probably the most useful
advice and
most constructive advice that I
have been

03:15.328 --> 03:17.097 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
able to give him.

03:17.130 --> 03:19.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: He said he hoped he
could take
a pause from politics, but made
clear he will

03:19.866 --> 03:22.402 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
