compelled to.

03:22.436 --> 03:28.842 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: Certain moments
where I think
our core values may be at stake.

03:28.875 --> 03:35.816 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I put in that category if I saw
systematic
discrimination being ratified in
some fashion.

03:35.849 --> 03:44.224 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Efforts to round up kids who
have grown up
here and, for all practical
purposes, are

03:44.257 --> 03:49.563 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
American kids, and send them
someplace else,
I think, would be something that
would merit

03:49.596 --> 03:51.331 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
me speaking out.

03:51.364 --> 03:55.735 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: And he weighed in one
last time
on an issue that has dogged
presidents for

03:55.769 --> 03:58.171 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
generations, the
Israeli-Palestinian conflict.

03:58.205 --> 04:05.512 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: If you do not have
two states,
then, in some form or fashion,
you are extending

04:05.545 --> 04:07.614 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
an occupation.

04:07.647 --> 04:12.486 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have believed, consistent
with the positions
that have been taken with
previous U.S. administrations

04:12.519 --> 04:21.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
