04:23.029 --> 04:27.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Mr. Obama also
reflected on how
America has changed during his
presidency,

04:27.334 --> 04:30.637 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
