vestige of slavery
and Jim Crow.

05:09.743 --> 05:16.283 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: This whole notion
of election
or voting fraud, this is
something that has

05:16.316 --> 05:18.818 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
