who are eligible
to vote who don't vote.

05:31.298 --> 05:35.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: As Mr. Obama, the
nation's first
black president, prepares to
leave office,

05:36.002 --> 05:40.607 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
