the future.

05:43.276 --> 05:47.647 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: If, in fact, we
continue to
keep opportunity open to
everybody, then,

05:47.681 --> 05:50.850 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
