Hindu president.

05:54.854 --> 05:56.723 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
You know what?

05:56.756 --> 05:59.226 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Who knows who we're going to
have.

05:59.259 --> 06:04.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I suspect we will have a whole
bunch of mixed-up
presidents at some point that
nobody really

06:04.364 --> 06:06.299 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
knows what to call them.

06:06.333 --> 06:11.271 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Once he becomes a
former president,
Mr. Obama says he is looking
forward to writing,

06:11.304 --> 06:13.039 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
being what he called quiet.

06:13.073 --> 06:17.811 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He said he doesn't want to hear
himself talk
quite so much in the future, and
also being

06:17.844 --> 06:21.915 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
