the subject
of news -- Judy.

06:21.948 --> 06:25.418 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: John, I also
thought it was
interesting that the president
acknowledged

06:25.452 --> 06:29.556 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
