context of a question
about inclusion and diversity.

06:35.695 --> 06:40.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He said it's important for all
Americans to
feel a part of the growing
economy.

06:40.533 --> 06:44.604 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
