and looked down
upon.

06:48.141 --> 06:52.445 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, John, you
had a busy day,
because I know, before the
president's news

06:52.479 --> 06:58.952 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
conference, you were -- you
attended a briefing
by the Trump transition team,
and they were

06:58.985 --> 07:00.887 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
