onslaught of EPA rules?

22:28.681 --> 22:32.218 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SCOTT PRUITT: Well, it's very
important that
that process be adhered to, to
give voice

22:32.251 --> 22:37.156 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to all Americans in balancing
the environmental
objectives we have, but also the
economic

22:37.189 --> 22:38.624 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
harm that results.

22:38.657 --> 22:41.961 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
