about that
rather consistently of late.

22:41.994 --> 22:46.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I would seek to lead the EPA
in such a
way to ensure that openness and
transparency.

22:46.632 --> 22:51.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Scott Pruitt is
expected to
confirmed by the full Senate,
with support

22:51.103 --> 22:53.973 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
from all 51 Senate Republicans.

22:54.006 --> 22:56.242 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm
Jeffrey Brown.

22:56.275 --> 23:01.247 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We also want to
follow up on
the confirmation hearing for the
president-elect's

23:01.280 --> 23:04.049 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
pick for education secretary,
Betsy DeVos.

23:04.083 --> 23:09.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
