23:45.591 --> 23:48.260 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BETSY DEVOS, Education Secretary
Nominee:
I think that's best left to
locales and states

23:48.294 --> 23:51.964 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to decide.

23:51.997 --> 23:53.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
If the underlying question is...

23:53.899 --> 23:55.634 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

23:55.668 --> 23:57.603 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRIS MURPHY: You can't say that
-- you can't
say definitively today that guns
shouldn't

23:57.636 --> 23:59.471 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
