23:59.505 --> 24:05.311 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BETSY DEVOS: Well, I will refer
back to Senator
Enzi and the school that he was
talking about

24:05.344 --> 24:07.212 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in Wapiti, Wyoming.

24:07.246 --> 24:13.419 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think probably there, I would
imagine that
there's probably a gun in the
school to protect

24:13.452 --> 24:14.553 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
from potential grizzlies.

24:14.586 --> 24:16.422 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

24:16.455 --> 24:20.292 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRIS MURPHY: If President Trump
moves forward
with his plan to ban gun-free
school zones,

24:20.326 --> 24:21.593 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
