24:21.627 --> 24:25.764 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BETSY DEVOS: I will support what
the president-elect
does.

24:25.798 --> 24:34.606 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, Senator, if the question is
around gun
violence and the results of
that, please know

24:34.640 --> 24:45.751 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that I -- my heart bleeds and is
broken for
those families that have lost
any individual

24:45.784 --> 24:46.752 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
due to gun violence.

24:46.785 --> 24:48.520 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

24:48.554 --> 24:49.788 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRIS MURPHY: I look forward to
working with
you, but I also look forward to
you coming

24:49.822 --> 24:52.024 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to Connecticut and talking about
the role
of guns in schools.

24:52.057 --> 24:57.396 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
