best left to the states.

25:20.819 --> 25:22.621 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

25:22.654 --> 25:25.391 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TIM KAINE: So, states might --
