kids are being
treated?

25:30.396 --> 25:33.165 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BETSY DEVOS: I think that's an
issue that
is best left to the states.

25:33.198 --> 25:34.166 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

25:34.199 --> 25:36.068 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
TIM KAINE: Let me state this.

25:36.101 --> 25:38.604 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think all schools that receive
federal funding,
public, charter, or private,
should be required

25:38.637 --> 25:42.374 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to meet the conditions oft
Individuals With
Disabilities and Education Act.

25:42.408 --> 25:43.609 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Do you agree with me or not?

25:43.642 --> 25:47.079 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BETSY DEVOS: I think that's
certainly worth
discussion.

25:47.112 --> 25:48.080 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I would look forward to...

25:48.113 --> 25:49.081 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

25:49.114 --> 25:50.282 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TIM KAINE: So, you cannot yet
agree with me?

25:50.315 --> 25:52.217 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: That was at
