fairly serious.

27:09.061 --> 27:11.363 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Lisa, one
other thing.

27:11.396 --> 27:15.367 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
