Homeland Security

28:04.449 --> 28:05.417 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
positions.

28:05.450 --> 28:06.852 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Those are the most important to
Republicans.

28:06.885 --> 28:09.955 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We will see if any of those are
confirmed
on day one.

28:09.988 --> 28:14.393 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Those are all -- all of that is
in the air
even just two days out from
inauguration.

28:14.426 --> 28:17.296 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
